设二维随机向量$(X,Y)$的联合概率密度为$f(x,y)=\begin{cases}k,&0<x<1,x^2<y<1\text{;}\\0,&\text{其他}\end{cases}$其中$k>0$为常数，下例结论正确的为:____
A. $$
f_X(x)=\left\{\begin{array}{l}
k\left(1-x^2\right), 0<x<1, \\
0, \quad \text { 其他. }
\end{array} ; f_Y(y)=\left\{\begin{array}{l}
k \sqrt{y}, 0<y<1, \\
0, \quad \text { 其他. }
\end{array}\right.\right.
$$
B. $$
f_X(x)=\left\{\begin{array}{l}
k\left(x^2-1\right), 0<x<1, \\
0, \quad \text { 其他 }
\end{array} ; f_Y(y)=\left\{\begin{array}{l}
k \sqrt{y}, 0<y<1, \\
0, \quad \text { 其他 }
\end{array}\right.\right.
$$
C. $$
f_X(x)=\left\{\begin{array}{l}
k\left(1-y^2\right), 0<x<1, \\
0, \quad \text { 其他 }
\end{array} ; f_Y(y)=\left\{\begin{array}{l}
k \sqrt{x}, 0<y<1, \\
0, \quad \text { 其他 }
\end{array}\right.\right.
$$
D. $$
f_X(x)=\left\{\begin{array}{l}
\left(1-x^2\right), 0<x<1, \\
0, \quad \text { 其他 }
\end{array} ; f_Y(y)=\left\{\begin{array}{l}
k \sqrt{y}, 0<y<1, \\
0, \quad \text { 其他 }
\end{array}\right.\right.
$$

class Employee
{
private:
int a;
protected:
int b;
public:
int c;
void display();
};
class Director:public Employee
{
public:
void show();
};
在C++中，以下操作正确的是____。
A. void Employee::show(){cout<<a<<b<<c<<endl;}
B. void Director::display(){cout<<a<<b<<c<<endl;}
C. void Director::show(){cout<<a<<b<<c<<endl;}
D. void Director::show(){cout<<b<<c<<endl;};

